description: We specialize in scratch made cupcakes in all flavors, shapes and sizes, for all occasions and events. Custom design requests are always welcome and we are happy to incorporate a special theme, color scheme or design into your custom cupcake order. Let us know if you have something specific in mind, and our creative team will come up with some ideas for you. Please contact us to schedule a cupcake consultation.Cupcake Delirium offers an assortment of cupcake stands and platter rentals. We will deliver, setup and pickup once finished. Please contact us for a price quote. Also please ask about our "Build a Cupcake Party" package. It's fun for all events and ages!
name: Cupcake Delirium
